      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "0. ADO child tasks — name each deliverable\n1. What is this story doing?     (plain English)\n2. Files to create / modify      (path + purpose)\n3. Data shape                    (IN → PROCESS → OUT)\n4. Connects to                   (prev + next story)\n5. Already set up for us         (interfaces, TODOs)\n6. Blocked / can't be tested     (name the blocker)\n7. What the docs say             (quote exact lines)",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "0. ADO child tasks — name each deliverable\n1. What is this story doing?     (plain English)\n2. Files to create / modify      (path + purpose)\n3. Data shape                    (IN → PROCESS → OUT)\n4. Connects to                   (prev + next story)\n5. Already set up for us         (interfaces, TODOs)\n6. Blocked / can't be tested     (name the blocker)\n7. What the docs say             (quote exact lines)",
      "lineHeight": 1.6
    },
